## TeamFlow Infrastructure Setup

### Database Configuration (PostgreSQL)
```bash
# Production PostgreSQL connection
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://username:password@hostname:port/teamflow_production

# Connection pool settings for production
DB_POOL_SIZE=20
DB_MAX_OVERFLOW=30
DB_ECHO=false
```

### Application Hosting
```bash
# Backend (FastAPI) - Railway
BACKEND_URL=https://teamflow-api-production.up.railway.app

# Frontend (React) - Vercel  
FRONTEND_URL=https://teamflow.vercel.app
```

### Environment Variables Template
```bash
# Core Application
SECRET_KEY=your_super_secret_key_here_minimum_32_characters
JWT_SECRET_KEY=your_jwt_secret_key_here_minimum_32_characters
ALGORITHM=HS256
ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRE_MINUTES=15
REFRESH_TOKEN_EXPIRE_DAYS=7

# Database
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:pass@host:port/db

# Security
ALLOWED_HOSTS=teamflow.vercel.app,teamflow-api-production.up.railway.app
CORS_ORIGINS=https://teamflow.vercel.app

# Features
DEBUG=false
ENABLE_SWAGGER=false
ENABLE_TEMPLATE_SYSTEM=true

# File Storage (AWS S3)
AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=your_access_key
AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=your_secret_key
AWS_STORAGE_BUCKET_NAME=teamflow-production-files
AWS_REGION=us-east-1

# Email (Optional for notifications)
EMAIL_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
EMAIL_PORT=587
EMAIL_USERNAME=your_email@gmail.com
EMAIL_PASSWORD=your_app_password

# Monitoring (Optional)
SENTRY_DSN=your_sentry_dsn_here
```

### Domain Configuration
```bash
# Custom domain setup (when ready)
PRODUCTION_DOMAIN=teamflow.app
